At AUTOBOLI LTD, we pride ourselves on delivering comprehensive auction data solutions to car dealers and traders across the UK. Our service is designed to empower your business with reliable, real-time data that enables you to make informed decisions and seize opportunities in the auction market.

Get Started

100% Data Solutions · Easy To Use · 100,000+ Vehicles

  • Real-time

Real-Time Auction Data

We gather and provide up-to-the-minute data from car auctions happening all over the UK. With our platform, you’ll have instant access to:

Current auction listings

Know what’s available for bidding as soon as it’s listed.

Live auction results

Get real-time updates on winning bids and final sales prices.

Auction schedules

Plan ahead by viewing upcoming auction events and key details.

This data is crucial for making fast decisions in a competitive market, and with our service, you’ll never miss a valuable opportunity.

  • INFORMATION

Comprehensive Vehicle Information

Each auction listing includes detailed vehicle data to help you evaluate potential purchases. You’ll get:

Make, model, and year of the vehicle.
Condition reports detailing any issues or damage.
Mileage and other important specs.
Starting and current bids to monitor price trends.

Having this level of detail allows you to make informed bids and find the best deals for your inventory.

Advanced Analytics and Insights

For businesses that require deeper insights, our Gold and Platinum plans offer advanced analytics tools. These tools allow you to:

Track market trends

See which vehicles are in high demand and adjust your buying strategy accordingly.

Analyze price trends

Use historical data to determine the right time to buy or sell.

Forecast future opportunities

With detailed trend analysis, you can anticipate upcoming market shifts and capitalize on them before your competitors do.

These insights can help you optimize your buying decisions, improving profitability and keeping you ahead of the curve.

Custom Alerts and Notifications

Time is of the essence in the auction business. With our custom alerts feature, you can:

1.

Set preferences to receive notifications when vehicles of interest are listed.

2.

Get updates on price changes or auction outcomes for specific vehicles.

3.

Receive reminders for upcoming auctions that match your search criteria.

Receive reminders for upcoming auctions that match your search criteria.

  • USER EXPERIENCE

Easy-to-Use Platform

Our platform is designed with simplicity in mind, making it easy for you to access and navigate through the data you need. Key features include:

Search and filter options:

Quickly find vehicles by make, model, auction house, or region.

Mobile-friendly interface:

Access auction data anytime, anywhere, from your mobile device.

Downloadable reports:

Export data for offline use or further analysis.

Whether you’re at your desk or on the go, our platform ensures that the information you need is always accessible.

  • SUPPORT

Dedicated Customer Support

Our customer support team is here to ensure that you get the most out of our service. Whether you have technical questions or need help interpreting data, we’re available to assist you. Gold and Platinum subscribers also receive priority support, with faster response times and dedicated assistance.
